  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Roadmaps</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/57839a8ddeff026c6416925b68f9c13d.avif?t=1756055669\" width=1560 height=867 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello everyone! PromiZed Land : Outer Town 2025 is now having a roadmap on progress. What's new? This game will be an Online Multiplayer where you can meet other investigator in lobby session. Beware, there will be various challenging game modes, be fashionist with new customization where you can get it in the game, also new avatar, zombies and other interesting map to dive in. Worry not, this will make a whole new look of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay tune and keep in touch! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/1e113a40c5c79629eafbcfaf7300fc6f.avif?t=1756055669\" width=640 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Synopsis</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Officer Gabriel, Sgt. Natalia & Col. John Tyson are investigating an abandoned town. Many residents claim it is a cursed place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As they investigate, they encounter inexplicable phenomena and struggle to survive in critical conditions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Game Mode</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in various mode starting from Investigation, Rescue, or Versus. No matter what you choose, zombie will chasing you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/2aedb07bb5af7aa627bd2f0b512e17c9.poster.avif?t=1756055669\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/2aedb07bb5af7aa627bd2f0b512e17c9.webm?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/2aedb07bb5af7aa627bd2f0b512e17c9.mp4?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Co-Op Split Screen</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your closest person or family, become a solid partner or challenge them to prove who's the badass investigator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/4a72f35ac867e1e02f533ca2012a875d.poster.avif?t=1756055669\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/4a72f35ac867e1e02f533ca2012a875d.webm?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/4a72f35ac867e1e02f533ca2012a875d.mp4?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigate the Anomaly</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A terrifed accident came to the Outer Town. Get your clues, find the way out, and survive from the living corpse in this cursed land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/a65f79930fc574f4c3f3bdcfabc4c681.poster.avif?t=1756055669\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/a65f79930fc574f4c3f3bdcfabc4c681.webm?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/a65f79930fc574f4c3f3bdcfabc4c681.mp4?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Save the Professor</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's a professor doing a research in the cursed land, however something bad happened, something not expected. Protect him and stay alive until rescue arrive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/e6e7a2eff772f78c6cffd3214faf8ca6.poster.avif?t=1756055669\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/e6e7a2eff772f78c6cffd3214faf8ca6.webm?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/e6e7a2eff772f78c6cffd3214faf8ca6.mp4?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compete your Partner</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your partner to prove who's the best investigator. Remember, no matter where you are, it's always zombie chasing for scar. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/ff5a76f256e59db1573157ce819cbcf8.poster.avif?t=1756055669\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/ff5a76f256e59db1573157ce819cbcf8.webm?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355610/extras/ff5a76f256e59db1573157ce819cbcf8.mp4?t=1756055669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PromiZed Land: Outer Town 2025</strong> is a third-person shooter horror simulator that takes you into a cursed land. Experience an immersive shooting game that blends excitement and thrill with moments of joy and satisfaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>#EnterTheCursedLand #LostInOuterTown </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Developer Notes</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PromiZed Land : Outer Town 2025 was an experimental project, however our passion drive us to make this game more than just a simulator. We will add more exciting feature where you will meet a thrilling and fun experience. We hope the upcoming updates will be realized as we expected. Thank you.</p>",
